205
00:25:54,155 --> 00:26:00,028
Framåt, Fläskis!
Skynda på, din stora skithög!

206
00:26:00,203 --> 00:26:05,493
-Räck mig handen! Jag har fastnat!
-Andas in.

207
00:26:05,667 --> 00:26:08,158
Dra in magen.

208
00:26:08,336 --> 00:26:11,705
