423
00:51:05,124 --> 00:51:07,532
Vi växte upp tillsammans.

424
00:51:10,338 --> 00:51:13,007
Vänta.

425
00:51:34,946 --> 00:51:37,271
Kom, Zico!

426
00:51:51,421 --> 00:51:53,912
Nej! Vänta, Zico!

427
00:52:20,366 --> 00:52:22,442
